<h1><span id="Pirc_Defence">Pirc Defence</span></h1>
<h3><span id="3.Nc3">3.Nc3</span></h3>
<p>White replies to Black's developing move with a developing move of his own, 3.Nc3. The move is noncommittal, as the knight was probably going to go to c3 anyway. It protects the e-pawn and maintains White's large center.
</p>
